  "short_description": "Turn the Line is a co-op tycoon game that allows 1~4 players. Cute characters, simple manual, but with difficult levels! Anyone can give it a shot, but not everyone can do it perfectly! Challenge perfection, so that the bunnies can leave work on time!",
